Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.85,0:01:48.73,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}EPISODE 5: PRISONER OF LOVE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.31,0:01:50.15,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.69,0:01:52.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Looks like you're awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.32,0:01:55.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Were we dreaming just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.24,0:01:59.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes. And this substance is dissolving us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.20,0:02:00.45,Main,,0,0,0,,In this very room.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.95,0:02:02.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Please break down the door…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.99,0:02:05.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Use your ability, Star Platinum.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.75,0:02:09.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.34,0:02:17.26,Main,,0,0,0,,You did it! Now drag me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.34,0:02:19.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.68,0:02:20.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.26,0:02:23.22,Main,,0,0,0,,What did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.30,0:02:25.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Did you say "Star Platinum"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.27,0:02:26.60,Main,,0,0,0,,That's my Stand name.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.02,0:02:30.65,Main,,0,0,0,,How do you know that, Jolyne?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.23,0:02:32.44,Main,,0,0,0,,From the looks of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.02,0:02:35.90,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}we started dreaming\Nafter I told you about Johngalli A.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.48,0:02:37.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Which means
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.28,0:02:40.86,Main,,0,0,0,,you haven't seen my Stand ability yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.53,0:02:44.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Since we are related,\Nyou may be feeling its presence,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.78,0:02:47.08,Main,,0,0,0,,but you couldn't have known its name.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.91,0:02:51.62,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not adding up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.34,0:02:55.25,Main,,0,0,0,,This is
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.84,0:02:56.96,Main,,0,0,0,,not reality!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.97,0:03:09.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Stone Free…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.19,0:03:11.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Jolyne.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.69,0:03:14.48,Main,,0,0,0,,You finally woke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.56,0:03:15.90,Main,,0,0,0,,That took too much effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.61,0:03:18.11,Main,,0,0,0,,My thread melts fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.69,0:03:21.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Jolyne… You were dreaming too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.91,0:03:23.99,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know about yours,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.07,0:03:26.37,Main,,0,0,0,,but mine was a terrible nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.45,0:03:27.41,Main,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.04,0:03:30.83,Main,,0,0,0,,So we were both dreaming
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.91,0:03:32.25,Main,,0,0,0,,as if watching a movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.33,0:03:36.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Guess so. It would've been perfect\Nif only we had some popcorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.84,0:03:39.71,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't move anymore. Not even a finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.80,0:03:42.68,Main,,0,0,0,,What about you? Can you move?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.76,0:03:44.43,Main,,0,0,0,,What we are perceiving
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.18,0:03:47.01,Main,,0,0,0,,could still be a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.89,0:03:50.73,Main,,0,0,0,,If you can't move at all,\Nthen we're awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.35,0:03:53.27,Main,,0,0,0,,We are in this reality
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.35,0:03:55.10,Main,,0,0,0,,where we can't escape this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.19,0:03:56.02,Main,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.61,0:03:59.23,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll die at this rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.15,0:04:01.65,Main,,0,0,0,,The charm's ability…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.53,0:04:04.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Show me the ability you used\Nto wake me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.20,0:04:07.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Stone Free.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.74,0:04:10.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes. Can you materialize it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.83,0:04:12.29,Main,,0,0,0,,I mean your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.37,0:04:14.79,Main,,0,0,0,,I understand, but it's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.87,0:04:17.13,Main,,0,0,0,,It was hard enough to wake you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.21,0:04:19.05,Main,,0,0,0,,No way could I break down the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.13,0:04:21.01,Main,,0,0,0,,No, just materialize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.80,0:04:28.10,Main,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.76,0:04:29.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.39,0:04:32.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Can you bring it out a bit more?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.31,0:04:36.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Move it slightly towards me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.31,0:04:40.69,Main,,0,0,0,,It'd be best if you could move it\Na bit more to the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.99,0:04:43.61,Main,,0,0,0,,This will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.70,0:04:45.99,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not ideal, but it's close enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.78,0:04:49.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Now we can leave this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.92,0:05:02.92,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}That was my Stand, "Star Platinum."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.51,0:05:07.01,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Pull me out. This isn't a dream.\NI'm certain of it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.09,0:05:09.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Damn you…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.97,0:05:13.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Bullshit…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.93,0:05:17.35,Main,,0,0,0,,It hurts and I'm pissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.44,0:05:19.52,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you hit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.15,0:05:22.57,Main,,0,0,0,,We got out, but I'm pissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.65,0:05:24.90,Main,,0,0,0,,We're definitely not dreaming, all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.58,0:05:37.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, give me your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.92,0:05:39.17,Main,,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.63,0:05:44.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.26,0:05:46.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.38,0:05:48.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you know what this is?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.59,0:05:52.14,Main,,0,0,0,,This bone saved our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.64,0:05:53.72,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a human bone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.60,0:05:55.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Plus,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.14,0:05:59.31,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}it's the sacrum from\Nthe pelvic area of an adult female.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.40,0:06:03.48,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Its surface looks like\Nit was dissolved with some kind of acid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.57,0:06:04.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Dissolved?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.94,0:06:06.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Is that what was used on us?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.69,0:06:07.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Can't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.24,0:06:11.82,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know why you have that bone,\Nbut it doesn't matter now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.91,0:06:13.79,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was the only one who saw that boy,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.87,0:06:15.58,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but he's definitely here!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.66,0:06:18.54,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's a mystery,{\i}\N{\i1}but he's within these prison walls!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.42,0:06:24.13,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Code 909, emergency level 4.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.21,0:06:26.80,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Emergency alarm activated{\i}\N{\i1}in the visitation room.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.88,0:06:29.26,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Emergency level 4, code 909.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.34,0:06:30.89,Main,,0,0,0,,What's your plan now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.97,0:06:33.76,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess now you're a criminal too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.85,0:06:35.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Like I told you,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.64,0:06:37.18,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm breaking you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.81,0:06:39.85,Main,,0,0,0,,You have the charm, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.40,0:06:45.90,Main,,0,0,0,,It's crucial that you hold onto it.\NDon't lose it, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.61,0:06:49.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's go. We're leaving this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.58,0:07:04.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Who would have thought that\Nthey would be able to escape this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.71,0:07:11.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Is it just me?\NI don't see that many guards.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.22,0:07:13.01,Main,,0,0,0,,This is a common area.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.76,0:07:15.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.18,0:07:20.69,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll escape through the window\Nmarked with an X.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.44,0:07:23.52,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This window faces the beach.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.60,0:07:26.52,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We'll board a submarine at the beach{\i}\N{\i1}to escape this island.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.11,0:07:28.36,Main,,0,0,0,,A submarine?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.44,0:07:30.86,Main,,0,0,0,,I have an amicable relationship\Nwith a group
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.95,0:07:32.91,Main,,0,0,0,,called The Speedwagon Foundation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.99,0:07:34.82,Main,,0,0,0,,They have provided our way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.54,0:07:49.26,Main,,0,0,0,,There doesn't seem to be\Na camera in this hallway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.34,0:07:51.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Our target window is one left turn away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.63,0:07:54.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Then we'll be about 20m\Naway from the shore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.93,0:07:58.01,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sure there is a lot to consider,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.10,0:07:59.89,Main,,0,0,0,,but let's get out of here first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.73,0:08:02.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.53,0:08:11.28,Main,,0,0,0,,It's just the fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.36,0:08:12.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Jolyne.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.16,0:08:24.75,Main,,0,0,0,,It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.29,0:08:27.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Where are you looking? Stay calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.21,0:08:29.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.63,0:08:36.76,Main,,0,0,0,,What's the matter? Give me your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.84,0:08:39.14,Main,,0,0,0,,It's just that…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.22,0:08:41.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, thanks,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.22,0:08:43.39,Main,,0,0,0,,but I can stand up by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.48,0:08:44.73,Main,,0,0,0,,That's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.81,0:08:48.11,Main,,0,0,0,,You almost lost this.\NBe careful when you trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.19,0:08:50.94,Main,,0,0,0,,I told you not to lose this charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.45,0:08:55.49,Main,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.16,0:08:57.62,Main,,0,0,0,,I told you it's important.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.28,0:09:00.12,Main,,0,0,0,,You must hold onto it. Take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.41,0:09:05.87,Main,,0,0,0,,You're headed to Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.96,0:09:09.04,Main,,0,0,0,,This is your daughter we're talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.13,0:09:10.59,Main,,0,0,0,,And you call yourself her father?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.21,0:09:12.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Hello? Are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.30,0:09:20.14,Main,,0,0,0,,You haven't changed a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.22,0:09:23.22,Main,,0,0,0,,You're calm and collected as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.31,0:09:26.06,Main,,0,0,0,,When I almost died from a fever,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.14,0:09:28.15,Main,,0,0,0,,you didn't come home to check on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.23,0:09:31.44,Main,,0,0,0,,When I drove a car for fun\Nand was accused of theft,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.28,0:09:35.19,Main,,0,0,0,,you took a plane to Tokyo instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.95,0:09:38.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Right. As long as I'm safe,\Nyou don't care, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.54,0:09:46.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Even now, I'm just a troublemaker\Nthat doesn't get hurt even if I fall! See?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.91,0:09:48.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Lucky me, no harm done! Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.25,0:09:50.79,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.38,0:09:55.51,Main,,0,0,0,,If it's that important, hold it yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.26,0:09:58.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.18,0:09:59.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Shut up. I don't want it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.68,0:10:02.05,Main,,0,0,0,,That's not it. Something is off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.06,0:10:05.64,Main,,0,0,0,,We're being quietly followed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.35,0:10:07.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Jolyne, duck.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.58,0:10:25.75,Main,,0,0,0,,There's no one over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.83,0:10:27.71,Main,,0,0,0,,They might have headed the other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.79,0:10:29.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's just a guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.38,0:10:33.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, look closely!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.42,0:10:35.55,Main,,0,0,0,,The door is bent!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.05,0:10:38.84,Main,,0,0,0,,The convicts have come this far!\NWe are at--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.15,0:10:52.98,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}That's…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.53,0:10:59.28,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Johngalli A.!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.07,0:11:04.49,Main,,0,0,0,,That bastard…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.58,0:11:06.74,Main,,0,0,0,,He's here to finish us off himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.24,0:11:09.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Jolyne! Head towards the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.66,0:11:11.00,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll take care of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.71,0:11:15.50,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's Johngalli A.'s Stand!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.00,0:11:18.38,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But the only time{\i}\N{\i1}he ambushed us was in a dream.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.46,0:11:20.68,Main,,0,0,0,,-Die!\N-Are we still dreaming?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.05,0:11:27.14,Main,,0,0,0,,No! This is reality!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.22,0:11:29.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Time stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.11,0:11:37.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Our enemies…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.15,0:11:38.03,Main,,0,0,0,,There are…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.07,0:11:40.28,Main,,0,0,0,,two of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.28,0:11:43.20,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not only did he force us to dream,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.28,0:11:44.41,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but he showed us{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.99,0:11:47.66,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Johngalli A.'s actual Stand within it!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.20,0:11:51.25,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They had been preparing for this moment.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.33,0:11:52.75,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The moment{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.83,0:11:55.25,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have no choice{\i}\N{\i1}but to use my Stand ability{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.33,0:11:56.84,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to protect my daughter!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.84,0:11:59.30,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Their target{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.38,0:12:01.09,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}was me all along!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.17,0:12:02.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Time will move again. Jolyne!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.31,0:12:12.69,Main,,0,0,0,,You were one move behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.77,0:12:15.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Kujo Jotaro, I have been waiting
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.44,0:12:17.73,Main,,0,0,0,,for this moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.32,0:12:29.99,Main,,0,0,0,,It was just ready for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.08,0:12:31.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.37,0:12:36.46,Main,,0,0,0,,I finally got what I've been after\Nfrom Jotaro, the invincible Stand User!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.54,0:12:39.67,Main,,0,0,0,,This is Whitesnake's ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.09,0:12:43.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Those bullets!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.55,0:12:49.64,Main,,0,0,0,,The Stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.06,0:12:56.90,Main,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.98,0:12:59.77,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought we only saw\Nhis Stand in our dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.86,0:13:02.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Anyway, while he can't shoot, I'll…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.39,0:13:30.51,Main,,0,0,0,,I see the shore! We're close!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.47,0:13:32.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Go on without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.64,0:13:34.73,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll catch up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.52,0:13:36.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Were you actually…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.73,0:13:38.73,Main,,0,0,0,,shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.73,0:13:43.65,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Listen to me.\NA Stand User only controls one Stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.73,0:13:46.11,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}This means we are up against two enemies,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.11,0:13:51.24,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Johngalli A. and the one\Nwho tried to dissolve us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.21,0:13:59.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.63,0:14:01.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Take this charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.75,0:14:02.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't drop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.84,0:14:06.55,Main,,0,0,0,,A transmitter is implanted within it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.63,0:14:08.34,Main,,0,0,0,,It's there to track your location.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.30,0:14:14.56,Main,,0,0,0,,The submarine is honed\Nto follow the GPS signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.14,0:14:17.31,Main,,0,0,0,,You understand what I'm saying, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.10,0:14:21.56,Main,,0,0,0,,All you have to do is go to the beach.\NThe submarine will come to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.15,0:14:26.86,Main,,0,0,0,,And The Speedwagon Foundation\NI told you about will find you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.49,0:14:33.20,Main,,0,0,0,,If you understand, then go, Jolyne.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.16,0:14:35.16,Main,,0,0,0,,This charm…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.95,0:14:37.71,Main,,0,0,0,,But earlier, you…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.79,0:14:39.83,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}No. You couldn't have…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.71,0:14:44.34,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I've always cared about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.84,0:14:52.89,Main,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.97,0:14:54.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Your chest… You're not…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.47,0:14:57.02,Main,,0,0,0,,No, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.60,0:14:59.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Go, Jolyne.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.18,0:15:01.06,Main,,0,0,0,,It's just a little blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.15,0:15:02.48,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll catch up soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.56,0:15:03.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.77,0:15:06.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Earlier, you sacrificed yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.78,0:15:08.94,Main,,0,0,0,,and the enemy took something from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.57,0:15:12.41,Main,,0,0,0,,That's why you couldn't\Nevade the bullets, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.12,0:15:14.20,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}What did he take?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.28,0:15:16.87,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Don't tell me… your Stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.29,0:15:20.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Jolyne!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.55,0:15:28.38,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.80,0:15:32.55,Main,,0,0,0,,These are…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.64,0:15:34.22,Main,,0,0,0,,These threads!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.30,0:15:35.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Since when?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.47,0:15:37.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.36,0:15:45.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.11,0:15:50.19,Main,,0,0,0,,We're about to leave from this window\Nand head for the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.86,0:15:53.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't get in our way. Got that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.78,0:15:55.37,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.95,0:15:58.54,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When did she acquire such a Stand ability?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.62,0:16:00.33,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}An ability of this strength{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.41,0:16:03.71,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}should have been reported{\i}\N{\i1}before her sentencing!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.92,0:16:07.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Very well. I will drop my gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.60,0:16:21.43,Main,,0,0,0,,I wasn't asking you to drop your gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.52,0:16:23.77,Main,,0,0,0,,I was just looking for the best angle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.85,0:16:26.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Your body's best angle to punch, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.61,0:16:31.28,Main,,0,0,0,,I only like it when your chin\Nis tilted slightly to the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.86,0:16:32.99,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just now,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.07,0:16:36.66,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I should have finished her first{\i}\N{\i1}instead of Jotaro!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.28,0:16:39.70,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Jotaro wasn't the one{\i}\N{\i1}I should've gone for first.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.29,0:16:43.50,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Does Whitesnake know about this?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.08,0:16:45.71,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kujo Jolyne.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.79,0:16:48.71,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Without a doubt, she is Kujo Jotaro's…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.79,0:16:50.21,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's a Joestar!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.09,0:16:55.26,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Jolyne.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.34,0:16:58.39,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Back then, in that dream…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.14,0:17:01.35,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}you said you'll stay behind at this jail{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.06,0:17:04.02,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}for some child you barely just met.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.60,0:17:07.10,Main,,0,0,0,,He grabbed my arm\Nwith desperation in his eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.19,0:17:09.11,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm going back inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.19,0:17:11.73,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was a mere dream I saw.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.40,0:17:14.28,Main,,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.91,0:17:22.75,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.83,0:17:25.50,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Dammit, we're so close to the beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.08,0:17:28.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.09,0:17:32.84,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Find them!{\i} {\i1}We have permission to shoot!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.92,0:17:34.67,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A guard has been shot.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.76,0:17:36.30,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The convict is armed.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.97,0:17:38.59,Main,,0,0,0,,We can shoot to kill!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.14,0:17:43.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Where is it? I'm at the beach already.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.89,0:17:46.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Where are they?\NThat organization you're friends with,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.64,0:17:49.10,Main,,0,0,0,,called The Speedwagon Foundation…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.19,0:17:50.56,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know who they are,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.15,0:17:53.98,Main,,0,0,0,,but if they really did send us\Na submarine,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.78,0:17:58.95,Main,,0,0,0,,then they must have incredibly\Nadvanced technology and financial power!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.53,0:18:02.41,Main,,0,0,0,,A gunshot wound like this…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.49,0:18:07.41,Main,,0,0,0,,This foundation must be able to administer\Nthe care you need better than anyone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.50,0:18:09.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Where is the submarine?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.71,0:18:11.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.06,0:18:26.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Everything you said was true.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.06,0:18:29.44,Main,,0,0,0,,The submarine is already at the beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.52,0:18:30.65,Main,,0,0,0,,We're saved…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.29,0:18:49.96,Main,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.17,0:18:53.00,Main,,0,0,0,,You can't…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.59,0:18:56.26,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, this can't be happening.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.34,0:18:58.34,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, this isn't happening.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.42,0:19:01.84,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He was shot, but it wasn't deep.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.93,0:19:03.68,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's not a fatal wound.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.47,0:19:07.93,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It can't be a fatal wound.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.02,0:19:08.85,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.27,0:19:12.06,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then his heart…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.31,0:19:16.57,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why isn't it beating?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.07,0:19:25.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.83,0:19:27.83,Main,,0,0,0,,The Joestar blood runs in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.91,0:19:31.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Jolyne, with your strong conviction,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.42,0:19:33.50,Main,,0,0,0,,I know you'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.58,0:20:09.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Found them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.62,0:20:12.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Something's moving\Non the other side of the fence!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.12,0:20:13.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Watch for the gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.67,0:20:16.92,Main,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not outside the fence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.71,0:20:18.96,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm right here
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.05,0:20:20.63,Main,,0,0,0,,if you're looking for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.68,0:20:24.59,Main,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.68,0:20:25.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Hold, don't shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.30,0:20:27.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Her hands are up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.55,0:20:29.43,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}-But…\N-Don't shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.51,0:20:30.52,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}She's unarmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.60,0:20:32.68,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Are you surrendering?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.73,0:20:37.65,Main,,0,0,0,,There must be another man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.15,0:20:40.82,Main,,0,0,0,,A tall man who visited her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.90,0:20:42.90,Main,,0,0,0,,He must be nearby. Find him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.41,0:20:48.95,Main,,0,0,0,,That's where you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.87,0:20:56.88,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.63,0:20:59.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you run?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.29,0:21:02.42,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry,\Nbut your father is already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.76,0:21:08.35,Main,,0,0,0,,His spirit was stolen by that sludge.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.85,0:21:11.39,Main,,0,0,0,,You barely managed to survive!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.47,0:21:14.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you leave? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.98,0:21:18.31,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The murderer escaped inside the prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.40,0:21:20.02,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Not outside, inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.32,0:21:24.99,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The murderer had planned to steal{\i}\N{\i1}my father's Stand by giving it form.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.07,0:21:25.95,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's his ability!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.03,0:21:30.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Then the murderer retreated\Nback into the prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.28,0:21:31.83,Main,,0,0,0,,He won't leave this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.91,0:21:34.79,Main,,0,0,0,,He is within these walls!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.87,0:21:38.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you actually trying\Nto get his ability back?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.54,0:21:40.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you think it'll bring him back to life?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.79,0:21:43.05,Main,,0,0,0,,That's precisely why\NI'm going back inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.09,0:21:48.59,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to say this,\Nbut a corpse will only rot away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.68,0:21:51.85,Main,,0,0,0,,That melted bone I gave you\Nbelonged to my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.93,0:21:53.52,Main,,0,0,0,,That sludge stole her ability
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.60,0:21:54.85,Main,,0,0,0,,and she died.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.60,0:21:57.44,Main,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.60,0:22:01.77,Main,,0,0,0,,My mom was an inmate here\Nand gave birth to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.27,0:22:04.74,Main,,0,0,0,,I grew up in hiding within these walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.40,0:22:07.36,Main,,0,0,0,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.45,0:22:10.28,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm Emporio.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.37,0:22:11.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Emporio.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.91,0:22:14.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Your mother's bone saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.20,0:22:16.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.34,0:22:24.46,Main,,0,0,0,,But,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.05,0:22:27.42,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't explain it, but I'm certain of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.51,0:22:30.18,Main,,0,0,0,,My dad's not dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.72,0:22:33.22,Main,,0,0,0,,If I get his Stand back,\Nhe will come back to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.26,0:22:35.35,Main,,0,0,0,,That's why
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.14,0:22:37.06,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm going back!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.15,0:22:47.19,Main,,0,0,0,,You've done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.20,0:22:51.82,Main,,0,0,0,,You finally acquired\Nthis powerful Stand which can stop time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.82,0:22:56.79,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yes, and I have you to thank, Johngalli A.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.37,0:22:59.75,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}We make a great team together.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.83,0:23:04.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Please take me to the men's prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.59,0:23:05.96,Main,,0,0,0,,I let my guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.59,0:23:12.05,Main,,0,0,0,,And have you seen my gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.14,0:23:12.97,Main,,0,0,0,,It's right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.48,0:23:26.07,Main,,0,0,0,,You're the only one who knows who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.65,0:23:30.24,Main,,0,0,0,,You shall be my scapegoat\Nfor the murder of the guards.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.32,0:23:32.91,Main,,0,0,0,,This way, everything works out peacefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.62,0:23:36.45,Main,,0,0,0,,To be able to communicate\Nsomething to someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.54,0:23:40.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Jotaro had said that is a wonderful thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.62,0:23:41.96,Main,,0,0,0,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.79,0:23:44.88,Main,,0,0,0,,And here, we have a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.09,0:23:48.92,Main,,0,0,0,,
